version_description:
-Multiplayer issues fixed
-All tiers in multiplayer are now free!!

-Overkill tournament update
-We've added a delete button to unfriend people from your friend list.

Want to know how Overkill 2 will feel like? Go to Medal store and enjoy free ammo for all your guns. Because in Overkill 2 there'll be free ammo for everyone! Overkill 2 is coming this March! Check www.overkill2.com for more. Follow us on Facebook.

We have just released Overkill 3. Our biggest and most daring shooter game ever!
Search Overkill 3 in the Appstore and try it out for free. It's sharp!

To raise the challenge we've locked the guns according to the difficulty of each level. Don't worry. You'll be able to upgrade your gun after each level.

-**Enjoy your Overkill 2 bonus!**
-Penalization for Multiplayer leavers

- Support for iOS 7
- New higher multiplier in survival (x14)! Get a higher score and push yourself to the top of the leaderboards!
- New graphics in medal store
- Bug fixes

Overkill now plays great on iPhone 6 and iPhone 6+.
iOS 8 Compatibility Update
